      "content": "Hey, I'm putting together a brief for my board regarding our long-term R&D roadmap. Can you give me a rundown of the main arguments people are making about whether we actually need heavy regulation on AI to prevent existential risks? I want to make sure I have the key points covered. Thanks.",
